Summary[edit]

DescriptionFlag of FLNKS.svg
Català: Bandera de Front d'Alliberament Nacional Canac Socialista
English: The flag of the Kanak and Socialist National Liberation Front political party, also used by the territory of New Caledonia alongside the flag of France.
Pantone colours as explained in http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/nc%7Dflnks.html by conversion in Commons:Pantone color chart.
Español: Colores Pantone http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/nc%7Dflnks.html y Commons:Pantone color chart.
Français : Drapeau du Front de libération nationale kanak et socialiste
Date 1 January 2006
Source Own work
Author User:WarX
